        "details": "<div class=\"value-sans\">\n<p class=\"blue-text value-sans\">Purdy &amp; Figg began with two best friends tired of using natural cleaning products that compromised on cleaning power.</p>\n<span class=\"gray-text value-sans\" style=\"color:#434448\">After spending five years in their garage, researching and formulating with PhD surfactant chemists, they created one powerful product that works on every surface, and is safe to use every single day, Counter Clean - now a viral sensation!</span>\n</div>"
